These are Puzzles for 1x3 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-3-1::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  coach, firefighter, designer
1. the designer is on the far left or far right##3
2. the firefighter is on the left of the designer##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |  2   |   3    |
| Job   | coach | firefighter | designer |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-3-2::.
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: october, february, september
1. the person who's birthday is in february is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person who's birthday is in september is in the middle##1
3. the person who's birthday is in september is on the right of the person who's birthday is in october##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |    1    |   2   |   3   |
| Birthday   | october | september | february |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-3-3::.
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: ice-hockey, basketball, swimming
1. the person who's sport is swimming is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person who's sport is swimming is on the right of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1   |  2   |  3   |
| Sport   | basketball | ice-hockey | swimming |

