.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-3-6::.
The people use 3 different means of transport: helicopter, car, snowmobile
1. the person driving the snowmobile is on the left or right of the person driving the car##3
2. the person driving the snowmobile is on the right of the person driving the car##1
3. the person driving the car is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |      3       |
| Transport   | helicopter | car | snowmobile |

